\s Nipe saa moja nawe Yesu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Nipe saa moja nawe \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  nikichoka huku duniani! Hata nikiona vita kali, wanistarehesha siku zote. \bd*
\pc \bdit Nipe saa moja nawe \bdit*\bdit Yesu\bdit*\bdit , kwani giza iko duniani! Natamani kukukaribia, kusikia neno lako zuri. \bdit*
